incompatible_content_explanation:
Google Play wants to provide safe and wonderful app experiences for our users and a great opportunity for all our developers to be successful.

You must complete account verifications in Play Console, including providing the following details:

  • D-U-N-S number, if registering as an organization
  • a phone number for Google Play users to contact you (organizations only)
  • an email address for Google Play users to contact you
  • a phone number and email address for Google to contact you
  • an official document to verify your identity
  • an official document to verify your organization (organizations only)
Visit Play Console Requirements and the Play Console Help Center for more information about developer verifications.
